Some are born CBe stars (fast\nrotators), as indicated by their presence in clusters younger than 10 Myr. Some\nstars evolve to CBe stars, as indicates by the enhancement in the fraction of\nclusters with CBe stars in the 20-30 Myr age bin.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Apr 2008 14:58:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
